const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What does your bi-monthly maid service include?",
    answer: "Our Bi-Monthly Maid Service follows the same proven Legendary Cleaning Rotating System as our weekly service, ensuring your home stays clean, fresh, and well-maintained between visits.\n\n• Every Visit – Bedrooms, bathrooms, kitchen, and living areas receive a full cleaning, including dusting, vacuuming/mopping, sanitizing, and wiping down surfaces.\n• On Rotation – Each visit also includes selected deep-cleaning tasks—such as baseboards, vents, cabinet fronts, or light fixtures—to prevent buildup in overlooked areas.\n• Optional Add-Ons – You can further customize your service with upgrades like:\n  o Cleaning inside the oven or refrigerator\n  o Refreshing shutters and blinds\n  o Changing linens\n\nThis service is ideal for smaller households, couples, or anyone who wants a consistently clean home without the need for weekly visits—while still enjoying the flexibility to add on extra detailing when needed."
  },
  {
    question: "Is bi-monthly cleaning enough for my home?",
    answer: "Bi-monthly cleaning can be a great fit depending on your lifestyle. Many clients with smaller households, empty nesters, or those who maintain their home between visits find it’s the perfect balance. With our Legendary Cleaning Rotating System, your essential spaces are refreshed every visit while deep-cleaning tasks are handled on rotation—so buildup never gets out of hand.\n\nIf your home has children, pets, or high foot traffic, you may prefer weekly cleaning for maximum consistency. During your free consultation, we’ll help you decide which schedule best matches your needs and lifestyle."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I request specific areas to be focused on each visit?",
    answer: "Absolutely. While our Legendary Cleaning Rotating System ensures a consistent routine, we also know that every home has changing needs. If certain rooms or tasks need extra attention during a visit, just let us know—we’ll prioritize them. You can also add optional upgrades like oven or refrigerator cleaning, blinds, or linen changes for even more customized care."
  },
  {
    question: "Will I get the same cleaner each time?",
    answer: "Yes. We do our best to assign the same trusted cleaner or team to your home for every visit, so you enjoy consistency, familiarity, and peace of mind. To ensure there are no interruptions, we also train a backup team on your home’s preferences. That way, if your regular cleaner is unavailable, you’ll still receive the same high-quality service and attention to detail you expect."
  },
  {
    question: "What happens if I need to reschedule a visit?",
    answer: "No problem! We understand that schedules can change. Simply give us at least 24 hours’ notice, and we’ll be happy to reschedule your cleaning at a time that works better for you—without any fees or hassle."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you have a cancellation policy?",
    answer: "Yes. We kindly ask for at least 48 hours’ notice if you need to cancel or reschedule a visit. This allows us to adjust our schedule and accommodate other clients. Cancellations made with less than 48 hours’ notice are subject to a $50 cancellation fee."
  }
